## Failure Handling

### Worker Crashes

If a worker crashes while processing:

1. Job remains in `processing` status with `claimedBy` set
2. `lastHeartbeat` stops updating
3. After `lockTimeout`, job is recovered (see [Heartbeat](/advanced/heartbeat/))

### Graceful Shutdown

When `stop()` is called:

```typescript
await monque.stop();
// 1. Stops accepting new jobs
// 2. Waits for in-progress jobs to complete
// 3. Clears claimedBy for any incomplete jobs
```

